      "text": "%md\n# Copy of import_test (2MPV94WZQ)\nCreated: 20260424_111914\n**Changes from source:**\n- All `%spark.pyspark` -\u003e `%python`\n- Reason 1: original failed because spark driver memory request 9011Mi exceeded zeppelin-qh\u0027s LimitRange limit 4Gi\n- Reason 2: spark-low fits memory but Spark startup fails on S3 history bucket access\n- Original paragraphs only do imports/pip - no actual SparkSession usage - so %python is functionally equivalent\n- Both interpreters use the same Python: /opt/zeppelin/packages/miniforge3/envs/ai/bin/python\n",
